        </p>
        <div
          class="mt-4 max-w-60 py-3 px-8 mx-auto border border-purple-500 text-center lg:text-right lg:float-right rounded-full space-x-1 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-500">
            <%= image_tag("play.png", alt: "play icon", width: "30", class: "inline-block") %>
